<item>
            <title>[LU-1213] Duplicate setting of mdtest_nFiles - parallel-scale.sh</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1213</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In parallel-scale.sh mdtest_nFiles is set on lines 69-71&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mdtest_nFiles=${mdtest_nFiles:-&quot;100000&quot;}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We devide the files by number of core&lt;br/&gt;
mdtest_nFiles=$((mdtest_nFiles/mdtest_THREADS/num_clients))&lt;br/&gt;
------&lt;br/&gt;
However, this is duplicated in functions.sh run_mdtest() lines 415-417&lt;br/&gt;
-------&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    mdtest_nFiles=${mdtest_nFiles:-&quot;100000&quot;}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We devide the files by number of core&lt;br/&gt;
    mdtest_nFiles=$((mdtest_nFiles/mdtest_THREADS/num_clients))&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Result: test attempts to use mdtest_nFiles/mdtest_THREADS/num_clients/num_clients - number of files is too small&lt;/p&gt;</description>
